<!--
  embed.html — minimal landing-page embed of the ROBIOS pipetting scene.
  Copy the <div>, the import map, and the module script into your page and
  host robot.js + anim.js next to it. No build step required.

  Even simpler alternative: use robios-pipetting.min.glb with <model-viewer>
